Dependancies:

Perl Module:
Time::HiRes
MIME::QuotedPrint
Net::Pcap

----
Don't forget to add /etc/rc.d/rc.floodmon to your /etc/rc.d/rc.local so that 
you can start floodmon at machine startup.
Do something like this

# Start floodmon server
if [ -x /etc/rc.d/rc.floodmon ]; then
	/etc/rc.d/rc.floodmon start
fi

